The Chartered Institute of Human Resources and Strategic Management (CIHRSM) is set to hold its bi- annual conference and induction of Fellows and Members on Saturday December 12 this year at Presken Hotel, Obafemi Awolowo Way, Ikeja at 10am. The theme of this year of conference is Managing Recession: HR/ SM Perspectives. According to the Registrar and CEO, Mr. Abell Minna,
CIHRSM of Nigeria is a professional body registered by the Federal Ministry of Education and other relevant agencies of government. He said the core mandate of the institute is to redefine human resources and strategic management principles and practice in Nigeria in line with global standards and best practices.